{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/update-font/","webpackCompilationHash":"94421e8e14387bb0e41a","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"A Developer, and a Cat","author":"Alex Yu"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"58fae247-be61-5076-a112-3915670d764f","excerpt":"Typography 一開始打完第一篇的時候, 發現字體看了不是很順眼. 由於沒有用過Typography, 所以不是很確定如何更換字體, google了一下發現有人說在加上google font的url並且在html加上font-family屬性[…","html":"<h3>Typography</h3>\n<p>一開始打完第一篇的時候, 發現字體看了不是很順眼. 由於沒有用過Typography, 所以不是很確定如何更換字體, google了一下發現有人說在<code class=\"language-text\">layout.css</code>加上google font的url並且在html加上font-family屬性<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/47488440/how-do-i-add-google-fonts-to-a-gatsby-site\">[1]</a>, 不過我試了發現沒有用,\n<img src=\"./html_css.png\"></p>\n<p>我猜原因是在<code class=\"language-text\">layout.js</code>裡面有設定了</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;h3\n\tstyle={{\n\t\tfontFamily: `Montserrat, sans-serif`,\n\t\t\tmarginTop: 0,\n\t\t}}\n\t&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>而且我不是很喜歡在這種直接在css裡面設定style的做法.</p>\n<p>所以我便看了一下Typography.js的官方文件, 有寫著<code class=\"language-text\">googleFonts</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">headerFontFamily</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">bodyFontFamily</code>的設定<a href=\"https://kyleamathews.github.io/typography.js/\">[2]</a>, 於是便在<code class=\"language-text\">src/utils/typography.js</code>裡面加上</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Wordpress2016.headerFontFamily = [&#39;Noto Serif TC&#39;, &#39;sans-serif&#39;];\nWordpress2016.bodyFontFamily = [&#39;Noto Serif TC&#39;, &#39;sans-serif&#39;];\nWordpress2016.googleFonts = [\n\t{\n\t\tname: &#39;Noto Serif TC&#39;,\n\t\tstyles: [\n\t\t\t&quot;400&quot;,\n\t\t\t&quot;500&quot;,\n\t\t\t&quot;600&quot;,\n\t\t\t&quot;700&quot;,\n\t\t\t&quot;900&quot;,\n\t\t]\n\t}\n];</code></pre></div>\n<p>便更改成功了,</p>\n<p><em>before</em>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5a7f01ad58444cff961cc8f87d4db7ae/ff64a/homepage-before.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.408284023668635%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"homepage before\"\n        title=\"homepage before\"\n        src=\"/static/5a7f01ad58444cff961cc8f87d4db7ae/b9e4f/homepage-before.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5a7f01ad58444cff961cc8f87d4db7ae/cf440/homepage-before.png 148w,\n/static/5a7f01ad58444cff961cc8f87d4db7ae/d2d38/homepage-before.png 295w,\n/static/5a7f01ad58444cff961cc8f87d4db7ae/b9e4f/homepage-before.png 590w,\n/static/5a7f01ad58444cff961cc8f87d4db7ae/f9b6a/homepage-before.png 885w,\n/static/5a7f01ad58444cff961cc8f87d4db7ae/2d849/homepage-before.png 1180w,\n/static/5a7f01ad58444cff961cc8f87d4db7ae/ff64a/homepage-before.png 1352w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><em>after</em>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d18d2ffd40d5422d7e55fd534a52af35/50151/homepage-after.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.90044576523032%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"homepage after\"\n        title=\"homepage after\"\n        src=\"/static/d18d2ffd40d5422d7e55fd534a52af35/b9e4f/homepage-after.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d18d2ffd40d5422d7e55fd534a52af35/cf440/homepage-after.png 148w,\n/static/d18d2ffd40d5422d7e55fd534a52af35/d2d38/homepage-after.png 295w,\n/static/d18d2ffd40d5422d7e55fd534a52af35/b9e4f/homepage-after.png 590w,\n/static/d18d2ffd40d5422d7e55fd534a52af35/f9b6a/homepage-after.png 885w,\n/static/d18d2ffd40d5422d7e55fd534a52af35/2d849/homepage-after.png 1180w,\n/static/d18d2ffd40d5422d7e55fd534a52af35/50151/homepage-after.png 1346w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><em>before</em>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/613e770463b2fd25cee3be917f70fe55/91670/blog-before.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 95.84615384615385%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"blog before\"\n        title=\"blog before\"\n        src=\"/static/613e770463b2fd25cee3be917f70fe55/b9e4f/blog-before.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/613e770463b2fd25cee3be917f70fe55/cf440/blog-before.png 148w,\n/static/613e770463b2fd25cee3be917f70fe55/d2d38/blog-before.png 295w,\n/static/613e770463b2fd25cee3be917f70fe55/b9e4f/blog-before.png 590w,\n/static/613e770463b2fd25cee3be917f70fe55/f9b6a/blog-before.png 885w,\n/static/613e770463b2fd25cee3be